From eb9be1f1e96a6002b67fd620c4128dcd11984758 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: deviprasad2002 <deviprasad2002@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Apr 2026 07:46:00 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] Add optional NGSPICE_DIAG_FILE JSON-Lines diagnostic hooks
 (Story I).

Introduce diaghooks (init/close, DIAG_EMIT) and wire NR iteration,
pn/fet limiters, gmin/source stepping, DIO load stamps, and post-LU
matrix pivot stats. Init from CLI main and shared ngSpice_Init.
Zero overhead when NGSPICE_DIAG_FILE is unset.

Made-with: Cursor
